Name: Blip
Description: Blips are short glitches with usually a symmetric 'teardrop' shape

Name: Whistle
Description: Whistles (a.k.a. Radio Frequency Beat Notes) have a characteristic 'W' or 'V' shape

Name: Koi Fish
Description: Koi Fish are similar to blip glitches, but resemble a fish with a head, fins, and thin tail

Name: Power Line (60 Hz)
Description: Power Line are narrow in frequency around 60 Hz and its harmonics (multiples of 60 Hz - i.e. 120 Hz, 180 Hz) and last 0.2-0.5 seconds

Name: Violin Mode Harmonic
Description: Violin modes are short glitches at 500 Hz and harmonics (multiples of 500 Hz - i.e. 1000 Hz, 1500 Hz)

Name: None of the Above
Description: This category is for glitches that do not look like any of the other categories
